{"tid":2083412,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人會對死亡之後而恐懼","createTime":"2020-06-28T17:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T05:08:24.000Z","uid":346691,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c3ec58fccd7d32b11c87cc72d51cad1009e43ccf","tid":2083412,"uid":346691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:10:41.000Z","msg":"細細個開始就會咁諗 死左之後會點 咩都冇曬 <br />\n懷疑自己生存係依個世界既每分每秒有咩意義 <br />\n會思考依個世界係咪真實存在既 跟住有種好強烈既恐懼感 會透過自殘黎叫返醒自己 <br />\n到依家可能隔幾個月就會處於依種狀態 <br />\n可能你會話點解冇啦啦會杞人憂天 但自己唔知點解會控制唔到 懷疑自己好似有啲心理疾病<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d93e0f69759b419bf3c9ee5b9fa94b506e7fe828","tid":2083412,"uid":62167,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:16:47.000Z","msg":"對未知有恐懼好正常<br />\n不過唔好自殘 唔會幫你搵到答案"},{"pid":"8c555097a266555a6e55f65ccdb013cc96467bdd","tid":2083412,"uid":304032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/13qZ2cO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F13qZ2cO.jpg&h=057fe7e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nvry3K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nvry3K.jpg&h=8af00b37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cdc14af7d7ec3eda07ed33611bd8943af9311307","tid":2083412,"uid":351498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:39:55.000Z","msg":"會呀<br />\n成日諗死後係咪合埋眼就乜都無<br />\n乜都睇唔到 諗唔到野<br />\n跟住就不安係度喊"},{"pid":"120a77d34e59c39a9918d3374517abfcca48af68","tid":2083412,"uid":346691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d93e0f69759b419bf3c9ee5b9fa94b506e7fe828","tid":2083412,"uid":62167,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:16:47.000Z","msg":"對未知有恐懼好正常<br />\n不過唔好自殘 唔會幫你搵到答案"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T18:04:11.000Z","msg":"係唔受控制咁自殘 我都唔想"},{"pid":"2162145918bd5834a923fd601d0cf193adaa9850","tid":2083412,"uid":346691,"like":0,"dislike":0